###Creating (and running) singularity images using GNU guix###

1) guixr pack -f squashfs -S /bin=bin <name of tool you need> bash glibc-utf8-locales tzdata coreutils procps grep sed 
2) Copy *squashfs to appropriate directory (maybe rename)
3) Add to nextflow.config:
singularity {
  autoMounts = true
}
4) Add container to process:
container = '<tool>.squashfs'


###Making sure piped command provide the correct exit state upon failure###
Before every piped command add:
set -o pipefail
